    # rebecca "Yeah, they must have started the primary qualifying matches outside."
    rebecca "Sí, debieron haber comenzado los partidos de clasificación primaria afuera."

# game/scripts/Events/locations/dressrosa/dressrosa_h5.rpy:216
translate spanish dressrosa_h5_e0445d8c:

    # rebecca "A lot of people will be filtered out until only the best in the tournament remain..."
    rebecca "Se filtrará a mucha gente hasta que sólo queden los mejores del torneo..."

# game/scripts/Events/locations/dressrosa/dressrosa_h5.rpy:217
translate spanish dressrosa_h5_028880a7:

    # player "I had no idea about that... I guess it makes sense, it must be pretty fun..."
    player "No tenía idea de eso... Supongo que tiene sentido, debe ser bastante divertido..."

# game/scripts/Events/locations/dressrosa/dressrosa_h5.rpy:218
translate spanish dressrosa_h5_a6c0bdf4:

    # rebecca "You think so? Well, it's not really like that... Do you know why they're so cheerful out there?"
    rebecca "¿Crees? Bueno, la verdad es que no es así... ¿Sabes por qué están tan alegres ahí fuera?"

# game/scripts/Events/locations/dressrosa/dressrosa_h5.rpy:219
